listitem.para:
                    All definitions have a { in the same line as the selector, all rules are defined in one row per rule,
                    the definition ends with a row with a single } in it. See the following example:


#Selector {
    width: 10px;
    height: 20px;
    padding: 4px;
}

                    If multiple selectors are specified, separate them with comma and put each one on an own line:


#Selector1,
#Selector2,
#Selector3 {
    width: 10px;
}
